1 gas is used or for use as those terms are defined in section 151(j)
2 of the motor fuel tax act, 2000 PA 403, MCL 207.1151.
3 (d) (c) "Leaded racing fuel" means that term as defined in
4 section 4 of the motor fuel tax act, 2000 PA 403, MCL 207.1004.
5 (e) (d) "Liquified petroleum gas" means that term as defined
6 in section 151 of the motor fuel tax act, 2000 PA 403, MCL
